Moreover, the χ 2 analysis for estimating the hypothesis of monogenic inheritance was performed following Sokal and Rohlf’s model [ 27 ] description as follows ( F , the actual mortality; n , the number of treated mites; p , the expected mortality; q = 1- p ; r , the number of the pyridaben concentration): X i 2 = ( F - p n ) 2 pqn \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
